data.description: Calling all BUYERS! First time, second time, investors, YOU NAME IT! Shake off the snow and settle down in this sweet and simple, split floorplan shelter! This quaint and cozy, ranch style, 3 bedroom home is well equipped to serve your needs whether you're entertaining guests or raising a family. This home has an AC from 2017 and updated double pane windows for added efficiency... not to mention the SOLAR PANEL system that comes with the home! So long power bills!! Call today to schedule your showing - this won't last long under $300k!
